{"tid":1137282,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"日出康城MONTARA累收逾1.8萬票　成近2年新盤票王","createTime":"2019-05-03T15:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T04:41:10.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"77d965a2944269751a7b4c5ba5d772181ebe9d61","tid":1137282,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"會德豐地產旗下日出康城MONTARA將於明天首輪開售500伙，項目今日下午2時截票。會德豐地產常務董事黃光耀表示，項目累收逾1.8萬票，超額認購35倍，創集團及今年入票紀錄，有信心明日可沽清。<br />\n<br />\n黃光耀說，項目餘下116伙，將視乎銷售情況全推，或有較大加價空間。會德豐地產市務助理總經理陳惠慈指，有70%入票買家是25至45歲人士；在地區方面，有60%是九龍區客，港島及新界區客人各佔20%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，同樣為明日開售，億京發展旗下大埔白石角海日灣II今日截票，累收逾700張票，超購約1倍，項目將於發售366伙單位。"},{"pid":"b2134babae162d3613de8c9095444bbd58b7b3e7","tid":1137282,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"弱智先會買康城盤"},{"pid":"e668dc6d7b264b2cff7d9686d25e2573b1ea40cb","tid":1137282,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b2134babae162d3613de8c9095444bbd58b7b3e7","tid":1137282,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"弱智先會買康城盤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"9952094283e042d0e04cdb763359ec2d9f781b66","tid":1137282,"uid":85223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2134babae162d3613de8c9095444bbd58b7b3e7","tid":1137282,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"弱智先會買康城盤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"你買左邊到？"},{"pid":"44c5b644051e90ebb14de37a0223ca0980f9626b","tid":1137282,"uid":143940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:48:31.000Z","msg":"係咪打錯，海日灣2 應該收左5000幾票"},{"pid":"f96fedaf9cf473badd2a9d29e39402eb5c33069f","tid":1137282,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44c5b644051e90ebb14de37a0223ca0980f9626b","tid":1137282,"uid":143940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20